Definition: visual impairment resulting from the retina becoming separated from the choroid in the back of the eye
Example: treated by photocoagulation
Synonyms: detachment_of_the_retina, detached_retina, visual_impairment, visual, impairment, resulting, from, the, retina, becoming, separated, choroid, in, back, of, eye, treated, by, photocoagulation
Category: noun.state
